'''Odile Gakire''' Katese uzwi nka KIKI, Umunyarwandakazi, ni umwanditsi akaba n'umuyobozi w'amakinamico, Rwiyemezamirimo akaba yarananditse igitabo cyitwa Igitabo cy'Ubuzima (Book of Life).<ref>https://www.intermissionmagazine.ca/in-conversation/in-conversation-odile-gakire-katese-and-ross-manson/</ref><ref>https://nowtoronto.com/culture/theatre/the-book-of-life-odile-gakire-katese-2</ref> 

== Ibyo yagezeho ==
Mubyo yagezeho mu [[Rwanda]] harimo gutangiza kampani ya mbere y'ingoma yabagore yise Ingoma Nshya Women Initiatives, kampani yambere y'ababyinnyi yabigize umwuga yise Amizero Dance Kompagnie, Iserukiramico mpuzamahanga ryambere ry'ibihugu mu [[Rwanda]] yise Festival Arts Azimuts, iserukiramico nyarwanda ry'ingoma [[Rwanda]] Drum Festival

Ububiko bwa mbere bwa Icecream yise Inzozi Nziza-Sweet dreams<ref>https://www.volcano.ca/odile-gakire-katese</ref>

== Ibihembo yahawe ==
yahawe igihembo cyambere cya League of Professional Theatre women's Rosamond Gilder/Martha Coigney International Award. <ref>https://frenchculture.org/performing-arts/4471-odile-gakire-katese-receives-first-gildercoigney-international-theatre-award</ref>

